# Cron alternative to the launchd job (Linux servers, or macOS if you prefer cron).
# Install with:  crontab deploy/crontab.example   (edit the path first)
#
# Runs the bot at 10:00 and 15:00 every day. The bot's internal daily cap and
# gaps keep volume safe even if it's triggered more often.
#
# EDIT the absolute path to match where the repo lives on the target machine.

0 10 * * *  /Users/etech/Desktop/zach-bot/deploy/run-daily.sh
0 15 * * *  /Users/etech/Desktop/zach-bot/deploy/run-daily.sh
